Punch/Nemesis Enforcer/Unitron/Scattershot:




Punch looked at the scanners, seeing the chase after Windlord made by his 
comrades.  He also noticed they were heading for the Cybertronian Fire.
He opened up a comm. link to three people.

"This is Punch, possible attack on the Cybertronian Fire.  Nemesis, Unitron, 
and Scattershot, you can fly, so you can get there fastest.  Head there 
immediately." Punch ended the link as the three robots responded by taking 
flight for South Africa.
